org.kocakosm.pitaya.util

Class Splitter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kocakosm.pitaya.util.Splitter

  • public final class Splitter
extends Object
    Splits Strings using a predefined separator. Instances of this class are immutable.
    Author:
    Osman KOCAK
    See Also:
    Joiner

      • limit

        public Splitter limit(int limit)
        Returns a new Splitter that will behave as this one except that it will limit the number of times the splitting pattern is applied. If limit is strictly positive, then the pattern will be applied at most limit - 1 times. If limit is non-positive then the splitting pattern will be applied as many times as possible.
        Parameters:
        limit - the splitting limit.
        Returns:
        a new Splitter with the desired configuration.
